data.description: Discover the perfect blend of space and style at 8208 S Kenwood Ave. This exceptional residence offers 5 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, providing ample room for comfortable living. Step inside to find the elegance of hardwood flooring throughout, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The thoughtful layout includes a finished basement and attic, offering versatile spaces that can be tailored to suit your needs. Whether you're looking for additional living space, a home office, or a recreational area, this home provides the flexibility to accommodate your lifestyle. Notably, this home comes with the added benefit of a new roof, seamlessly blending modern amenities with classic charm. Don't miss the chance to experience the comfort and allure of 8208 S Kenwood Ave - schedule your showing today!
